data.description:
Home Was Updated 3 Years Ago; Laminate Wood Flooring, Stainless Steel Appliances, Granite In Kitchen And Baths, Backsplash in Kitchen With Plenty Of Cabinets. Tile in Kitchen And Foyer, Vaulted Ceiling And WBFP In Living Room, Walk In Closets, Spacious One Car Garage.  Super Cute and Cozy House That Maybe Needs Just Some Fresh Paint.  Minutes From I30, Shopping And Restaurants.  
Seller Will Require Minimum Of 2 Weeks Leaseback.
